| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7307 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2072c42a-b395-5d85-adb2-dbf9cd7c4a28"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
